data.description: You don't want to miss this one! NO HOA under $320,000 & $5K in CC. Located in a cul-de-sac and neighborhood of just 13 homes, this hidden gem offers an open concept living space along with a private backyard oasis. Easy maintenance laminate flooring throughout the home plus a neutral color palette add to the overall feel of calm. You will love the kitchen with newer stainless appliances, plenty of cabinets and counter space, an island with space for 2 counter seats and TWO pantries. Laundry, powder room and garage access are off of the kitchen. Head upstairs to your Owner's Suite complete with access to a spacious deck through the en-suite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom complete the upstairs space. Enjoy outdoor living in your fenced in backyard complete with newBermuda grass, landscaping, a fire pit and large patio. Conveniently located to shopping, restaurants, schools, Interstate, Joint Base, Boeing, downtown Charleston and area beaches.
